### Global ###
##############

AddKeysToAgent yes

Host *
	ServerAliveInterval 60
	ControlMaster auto
	ControlPath /run/user/1000/ssh-%r@%h:%p.sock
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
	IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_rsa

### Computers

Host athena* hyperion*
	ForwardAgent yes
Host atlas*
	User root

### Third party hosts

Host codereview.qt-project.org
    Port 29418
    User hobarrera

Host *amazonaws.com
  User ubuntu
